-salat","tag-recommendation-al-mustahab","tag-sleep-al-nawm","tag-voluntary-prayers-salat-nafilah","tag-witr-prayer","tag-worship-al-ibadah"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-6BO","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":36388,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/30\/siyam-salat-al-duha-witr\/","url_meta":{"origin":25408,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Advice: Fasting, Salat al-Duha, Witr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 30, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: My beloved friend, the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, instructed me with three deeds I will never leave for as long as I live: fasting three days a month, performing forenoon prayer, and not sleeping until performing Witr prayer. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 722 Grade: Sahih\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28159,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/witr-beginning-middle-end\/","url_meta":{"origin":25408,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Witr: The Prophet prays Witr before dawn","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, would perform Witr prayer every night, either at the beginning, middle, or end of the night, finishing his Witr prayer before the break of dawn. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 996, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 745 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28161,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/make-your-last-prayer-witr\/","url_meta":{"origin":25408,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Witr: Make last prayer at night Witr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMake the last of your prayers at night the Witr prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 998, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 751 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28132,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/nawafil-witr-sunan-fajr\/","url_meta":{"origin":25408,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Praying Witr prayer, Sunan of dawn prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray at night, two by two, and make it odd with one cycle. The Prophet would pray two cycles before the morning prayer, so lightly as if the call to prayer were in his ears. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19432,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/06\/29\/night-prayer-two-by-two-witr\/","url_meta":{"origin":25408,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Qiyam: Night prayer is two by two, plus witr prayer","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 29, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe night prayer is performed two by two. If you worry that morning is near, pray one cycle as that will be your witr prayer.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 990, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 749 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi (authenticity\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28163,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/26\/pray-witr-before-morning\/","url_meta":{"origin":25408,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Nawafil: Pray Witr before morning comes","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 26, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cPerform Witr prayer before the morning.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 754 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e